# QUIZ APP - REFINED DESIGN DOCUMENT

## Executive Summary
A minimalist, educational quiz application that allows users to test their knowledge across multiple categories, create custom quizzes, and track their learning progress. The app focuses on simplicity, accessibility, and user engagement through gamification elements.

## 1. Product Vision

### 1.1 App Category
- Educational Tool
- Knowledge Quiz Game
- Interactive Learning Platform

### 1.2 Genre
- Quiz/Trivia
- Casual
- Educational

### 1.3 Core Value Proposition
An intuitive quiz platform that combines learning with engagement through:
- Clean, distraction-free interface
- User-generated content capabilities
- Gamification elements that encourage continued learning
- Cross-platform accessibility

### 1.4 Target Audience
- Students seeking study aids
- Educators creating learning materials
- Knowledge enthusiasts
- Casual users looking for mental stimulation

### 1.5 App Overview
The app presents users with categorized knowledge quizzes in a clean, minimalist interface. Users can select from predefined categories (Science, Math, History, etc.), choose difficulty levels, and take quizzes to earn points and achievements. Beyond consuming content, users can create and share their own quizzes, contributing to the platform's knowledge base.

